posts.body: Holy shit, she wasn't kidding about feeling braver.
We're pretty much up to date with her Only Fans. Not much to do but wait until she posts new sets. Thankfully it sounds like she's got stuff ready, maybe a week or so?

It's smart to not get hopes up. But, she does seem to be getting more confident about how much she does show. I'm not saying she absolutely will get it all out, but I wouldn't be surprised if she might be reconsidering things. People change.

Thank you!
I have always got time for Meg's shower candids.

It's only 'dying' for Nigri, I think? Meg's stuff is still shared pretty soon after they're posted. It's only content from Jess that seems to be dying out. But to be fair she's hardly posted anything new in the last year, compared to before. That and the quality of her content is  bad in comparison to everyone else.
What a great thing to wake up to, thanks for posting!
